<br>
Do you like class based?  picking a Ranger....Warroir...so on.  Or do you like skill based,  where you pick your skills,  and make your own class.  You could have a wizard that Specializes in Fire,  but also,  can wield a staff with proficiency.<br>
<br>
Or would you like a mix?<br>
<br>
I am just wondering about this.  I have started to design a online RPG,  and I even havea  graphics engine started.  But I am trying to come up with ideas,  and I firgured you guys could help me out.<br>
<br>
BTW,  This will probably never be a working product,  but it will give me something to play with while I am here.<br>
